text: Kudeyevsky () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kudeyevsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3,091 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Iglino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Kudeyevsky
